{"tid":950794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得聖誕老人其實好撚爽","createTime":"2018-12-21T19:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T00:00:10.000Z","uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbbbcf28795cfb667ff04efa565a3cd75230f74","tid":950794,"uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T19:57:14.000Z","msg":"今日行過商場見有聖誕老人坐係到搖啷啷，好死唔死佢執死人鬚遮唔坐佢條肥仔頸，令我醒返起其實佢現實都係個死肥仔<br />\n<br />\n聖誕節走出黎扮下聖誕老人，就有一班細路女坐大脾影相，又有年輕肉體比佢攬下搭下膊頭<br />\n<br />\n但私底下佢可能只係日日唔出街唔洗頭嘅油頭毒撚，比你係街到見到都會嫌佢阻街嘅死肥仔，依家佢肯定日日暗爽同期盼緊啲女女同佢招手，平時連女神口水尾都冇份食嘅佢，今日竟然有女女主動問佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可摸耳影相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n每同影一張相 佢就多一次抽水機會<br />\n唔好話咩員工守則唔可以身體接觸<br />\n我係佢都摸撚左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲未計有啲真係死廢老出黎搵下食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c2993fda96f2f03f1869a149b679fb436b1ab8","tid":950794,"uid":20448,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"有幾低鳩能先會覺得著住套閪衫係度呵呵呵一日會係爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896fb0fd2a0d87b41c623b586c57c9b9e96e2f82","tid":950794,"uid":172390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c2993fda96f2f03f1869a149b679fb436b1ab8","tid":950794,"uid":20448,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T19:59:02.000Z","msg":"有幾低鳩能先會覺得著住套閪衫係度呵呵呵一日會係爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T20:05:10.000Z","msg":"毒撚仔咪會 平時冇機會<br />\n依家自己埋身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a64f4edfcc50353e117332a8b33d4116de0c0ca","tid":950794,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"要終生監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}